Package: R.ComDim
Type: Package
Title: ComDim Analysis in R
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Francesc Puig-Castellví
Maintainer: Francesc Puig-Castellví <puig.francesc@gmail.com>
Description:
    Provides functions to run ComDim analysis.
    ComDim is a multi-block method that simultaneously considers multiple data 
    tables to find latent components that are common to all the tables as well 
    as those specific to each data table, along with the contribution of each 
    table to each component.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: methods
Imports: pracma, utils, ggplot2
Suggests: gridExtra, imputeLCMD, ica, MultiAssayExperiment, SummarizedExperiment
